# Huggingface Bolts

This is a collection of generic streaming and (micro) batch bolts interfacing
with the huggingface ecosystem.

**Table of Contents**

- [Huggingface Bolts](#huggingface-bolts)
  - [Usage](#usage)
  - [Usage](#usage-1)
    - [Text Classification](#text-classification)

